ey when it comes to crazy ideas.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"I feel like I’m getting a better understanding of the Rabbit Alien as the days go by.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"BEILI4","fadeOut":1.5}